      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/uaw-commits-40-million-organizing-us-auto-battery-workers-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国汽车工人联合会 (UAW) 周三表示，将承诺在未来两年内投入 4000 万美元来组织美国非工会汽车和电池工人。]]></description>
