      <title>沃尔格林 (Walgreens) 在道指蓝筹股中失去位置后股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/walgreens-shares-fall-after-losing-spot-blue-chip-dow-index-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，美国连锁药店运营商沃尔格林联合博姿 (Walgreens Boots Alliance) 的股价下跌 3%，此前这家美国连锁药店运营商将其在道琼斯工业平均指数的排名让给了亚马逊，这标志着该蓝筹股指数 2023 年表现最差的短暂时期结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/walgreens-shares-fall-after-losing-spot-blue-chip-dow-index-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 11:32:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
